<center><table border=0><tr><td><center><H2><font face=arial>that is great. hehe</font></H2></center>
<font face=arial size=2><b>Posted By:</b> <A HREF="/cgi-local/whois.cgi?Blain">Blain</a><br>
<b>Posted On:</b> 11:38 a.m. 17/4/1999<br>
<b>Subject:</b> that is great. hehe<p>
<br><center><img src="http://www.everworld.net/images/datel.gif" width=46 height=22 border=0><img src="http://www.everworld.net/images/dateblnk.gif" width=100 height=22 border=0><img src="http://www.everworld.net/images/dater.gif" width=306 height=22 border=0></center><BR><P ALIGN=CENTER><b>In Reply To:</b> <A HREF="http://www.everworld.net/cgi-local/forum/tarrew_marr.cgi?read=53" TARGET=_self>Lavastorms First Event!</A> (Hansette)
</STRONG><FONT SIZE=2 color=#F4D99F FACE=arial>
<P>> We had our first event in Lavastorm

<BR>&gt; yesterday. Here is how it went...
<P>&gt; First, we were being entertained by
<BR>&gt; new-comers to the area that ran from fire
<BR>&gt; elementals and trained them on others while
<BR>&gt; in the pass. We have been enjoying watching
<BR>&gt; people run from elementals (as well as our
<BR>&gt; selves, occasionally, when we are low on
<BR>&gt; mana).
<P>&gt; We decided it was time to have a quick event
<BR>&gt; in Lavastorm. The bid of one platinum piece
<BR>&gt; to see who could train the most elementals
<BR>&gt; in a specific time frame to the pass
<BR>&gt; (without magical help). The player must live
<BR>&gt; and get all the elementals into the general
<BR>&gt; pass area and then zone.
<P>&gt; Sinrae stepped forwards and proclaimed she
<BR>&gt; held the title of six. We thought that was a
<BR>&gt; bit low. We said as much and said it must be
<BR>&gt; at least ten the next time. In private tells
<BR>&gt; aside, we were laughing too hard to type
<BR>&gt; complete words.
<P>&gt; Later, Sinrae came barreling over a hill
<BR>&gt; followed by no fewer than... eleven
<BR>&gt; elementals. The elementals flowed over the
<BR>&gt; hill in a stampede. Unluckily for Sinrae,
<BR>&gt; she had become slightly disoriented and was
<BR>&gt; running the wrong direction.
<P>&gt; Watching her health, she was down to about
<BR>&gt; two bubbles left, when she got her bearings
<BR>&gt; and ran into the pass. She now holds the
<BR>&gt; current record of eleven fire elementals in
<BR>&gt; a train. She said she could get fifteen the
<BR>&gt; next time if we hold the event again.
<P>&gt; Comments from people in the area ranged
<BR>&gt; from:
<BR>&gt; "Holy sh#$!"
<BR>&gt; "What the hell was that?"
<BR>&gt; "Damn!"
<BR>&gt; "Was that on purpose?"
<P>&gt; Happy training!
<BR>
</FONT></td></tr></table></P>
